OL,3,CCharlie Elphicke has legal bill
OL,4,Creduced after libel battle with Sunday
OL,5,CTimes
OL,7,FFormer MP for Dover Charlie Elphicke
OL,8,Fhas had the amount of costs he has to
OL,9,Fpay the publisher of the Sunday Times
OL,10,Freduced after a High Court defamation
OL,11,Fclaim.
OL,13,FElphicke, who was jailed for two years
OL,14,Fin September 2020 after he was
OL,15,Fconvicted of sexually assaulting two
OL,16,Fwomen, sued Times Media Limited for
OL,17,Flibel over three articles published in
OL,18,FThe Sunday Times in 2018, including
OL,19,Ftwo which referenced an investigation
OL,20,Fof rape allegations against him.
