OL,3,CCharlie Elphicke has legal bill
OL,4,Creduced after libel battle with Sunday
OL,5,CTimes
OL,7,FThe former Conservative Party MP ended
OL,8,Fhis defamation case before it went to
OL,9,Ftrial in 2022, but asked to avoid
OL,10,Fpaying the costs of multiple
OL,11,Fapplications made by Times Media,
OL,12,Fsaying the publisher had "wiped"
OL,13,Fevidence.
OL,15,FTimes Media, which defended the libel
OL,16,Fclaim, made a bid for Elphicke to pay
OL,17,Fcosts.
