OL,3,CCharlie Elphicke has legal bill
OL,4,Creduced after libel battle with Sunday
OL,5,CTimes
OL,7,FIn a 51-page ruling on Monday, former
OL,8,Fjudge Victoria McCloud found Times
OL,9,FMedia failed to "preserve evidence" in
OL,10,Fthe case and that it was "appropriate
OL,11,Fto mark the seriousness" by reducing
OL,12,Fthe amount that Elphicke must pay to
OL,13,F80%.
