OL,7,FMs McCloud said Elphicke argued at a
OL,8,Fhearing in June 2023 that Times Media
OL,9,F"had lost or destroyed critical
OL,10,Finformation" that related to the
OL,11,Fallegations it made against him,
OL,12,Fincluding "the most serious matter
OL,13,F(that) was said to be the loss or
OL,14,Fdestruction of a journalist's
OL,15,Felectronic telephone information".
