OL,7,FIn the ruling, Ms McCloud said "the
OL,8,Fphone material would have clarified...
OL,9,Fwhether for example the complainant
OL,10,Fwas being inconsistent or whether
OL,11,Fwords were being put into her mouth or
OL,12,Fwhether there was another motivating
OL,13,Ffactor such as money, rejection, or
OL,14,Fpressure from anyone else".
OL,16,FThe former judge added that Times
OL,17,FMedia had "ample opportunity to
OL,18,Fpreserve the electronic information
OL,19,Fconcerned".
