OL,3,CCharlie Elphicke has legal bill
OL,4,Creduced after libel battle with Sunday
OL,5,CTimes
OL,7,FBut Ms McCloud ruled that Times Media
OL,8,Fhad "a duty to preserve evidence when
OL,9,Fon notice of proceedings or likely
OL,10,Fproceedings".
OL,12,FShe added that "failures to preserve
OL,13,Fevidence when on notice to do so, and
OL,14,Fwrongful collateral use of witness
OL,15,Fstatements" are "not matters which
OL,16,Frequire significant consideration of
OL,17,Fdocuments and attendance notes: they
OL,18,Fgo to the heart of the fairness of
OL,19,Fproceedings".
