OL,3,CCharlie Elphicke has legal bill
OL,4,Creduced after libel battle with Sunday
OL,5,CTimes
OL,7,FElphicke was found guilty of three
OL,8,Fcounts of sexual assault committed in
OL,9,F2007 and in 2016 after a trial at
OL,10,FSouthwark Crown Court in 2019.
OL,12,FAfter the ruling, Elphicke said the
OL,13,Fjudgment was "damning".
OL,15,FHe added: "It's unprecedented for any
OL,16,Fmedia business to be caught
OL,17,Fmisconducting themselves like this."
OL,19,FTimes Media has been approached for
OL,20,Fcomment.
